Articles.Content:
I have EL, MKS and SSPX along with a few other mods installed. SSPX is supposed to have an option to switch the cargo hold of it's logistics containers and storage modules to be able to hold rocket parts, and it does, however as soon as I installed MKS the EL resources disappeared from the menu and I could only choose stock resources, MKS resources and a few others. How do I fix this? Here's the log: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1BXrfkF9hE4OkokEcYpfAEAmdqZU4SqGu/view?usp=sharing and thank you for any support you can provide.

Edited May 27, 2021 by ayothepizza

Check in the MKS thread, there was something similar in there a few months back. But it sounds like MKS is overriding the resources set by EL. 

I also noticed you have some LGG mods that aren’t loading (hanger extender/better time warp) as they are missing the dependencies click through blocker and toolbar controller.

There is also something called “GU” which throws an error as it can’t find the data it needs.

You also have several miniAVCs which are now buggy so I’d get rid of those (or add the mod which blocks them for you).

All the mods work, I have no idea why errors are popping up. I also have all the dependencies. But thanks for the help
